mological data, we find, in particular, 95 percent limit on the\ntensor-to-scalar ratio R < 0.63 and on the fraction of massive neutrinos f_nu <\n0.11; we also obtain the 68 per cent confidence interval w=-1.06 (+0.20, -0.25)\non the equation of state of dark energy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Dec 2002 17:47:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 28 Feb 2003 14:09:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
